    "body": "## Problem:\r\nCurrently we are using\r\nif 1 item then\r\n  {title}: {percent}%\r\nelse\r\n  Progress: {AVG}%({N})\r\ndropping {title} and Progress text saves up space in statusline plus makes the format consistent, less jumping around.\r\n\r\n## Solution:\r\nUse {AVG}%({N}) on all cases for progress-status\r\n\r\ncc @justinmk ",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-26T09:47:17Z",
